  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Liver cirrhosis Child-Pugh-Score &gt; 7

          -  Ascites &gt; 500 ml

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Coronary heart disease

          -  Apoplexia &lt; 6 months ago

          -  Vasculitis

          -  Thrombosis

          -  Arterial occlusive disease &gt; stadium II
